author: AP
title: Belarusian club puts mannequins in stands as fans stay away
description: The defending champions in Belarus have started putting mannequins in the stands as soccer fans stay away from stadiums because of the coronavirus
content:
MINSK, Belarus (AP) — They don’t chant, they don’t move, and they mostly wear the wrong colors.
They’re not even real.
